 3- (ḥs bksry wbẓrwfy sẖạfy ạljrḥ lms kẖwfy)2
 hạḥky wạṣqf bkfwfy
 4- (knt bʿyd qrb mny sẖạfny wḥyd qạm ṭmny)2
 ʿmry mạ ḥạjẗ hạtạ̹lmny</lyrics>
